1. Datum vom Schluá des Briefes.

My dear Sir,

In compliance with your request conveyed in your note of the ult. I have
the pleasure to forward to you a proof sheet of your tract. I will thank
you to return it with such alterations as you may think it advisable to
make agreeable to your request 2000 copies shall be struck off immediately
on the receipt of the return proof sheet.

With kind regards believe me
.
                           Yours very sincerely
Cottuyam                       B Bailey
30th Decr 1841

